This misal outlet is located in Thane (W) behind sai baba temple at court naka.
Serving is good..as they serve in utensils made up of clay.
Also they got many varieties in Misal.
They have :-
Varhadi Misal ( Misal pav) 70/-
Misal Bhakri (Misal serve with bhakri)80/-
Misal shot (Misal gravy serve with pani puris puri) 80/-
Misal scotch (Misal serve with kachori)70/-
Dahi Misal , Vada Misal & even Jain Misal.
